!! title Rtn Get.Priv ;
! =========================================================================
=====================================+=====================================
=                                                                         =
=                                                                         =
=			       Rtn Get.Priv				  =
=                                                                         =
=                                                                         =
=====================================+=====================================


	Return the privilege word for a given frame.


